58
00:02:29,509 --> 00:02:31,967
with a bunch of hormonal teens
on a weekend trip.

59
00:02:33,373 --> 00:02:36,438
Anyway, I started feeling like I
was coming down with something,

60
00:02:36,473 --> 00:02:38,974
and... and then I got this rash.

61
