supposed to be on medical leave.

105
00:04:51,361 --> 00:04:53,595
I was, but my pain's
been at a consistent 3,

106
00:04:53,630 --> 00:04:55,931
and I've been off narcotics for weeks.

107
00:04:55,965 --> 00:04:57,499
